This is README file for Algorithm PA#3
Author: 張甡源 b11901123
Date: 11/22/2024
=====
SYNOPSIS:

cb inputs/<input_file_name> outputs/<output_file_name>

This program processes directed and undirected graphs, ensuring acyclic connectivity while optimizing edge weights using reverse Kruskal's algorithm and cycle detection.
=====
DIRECTORY:

src/main.cpp 
bin/cb
doc/report.pdf
makefile
README
utilities/checkSubmitPA3.sh

======
HOW TO COMPILE:

	Under the root directory of this PA, simply type
	make
======
HOW TO RUN:

	cd bin/
	./bin/cb inputs/<input_file_name> outputs/<output_file_name>
======
